none.description:
{Base Clarity}

A hero casts mass Mindshield (basic) spell at the begining of each battle.

Drains 20 mana per battle and lasts until next week.

basic.description:
{Basic Clarity}

A hero casts mass Mindshield (basic) at the begining of each battle.

Costs 10 mana per battle and lasts until next week.

advanced.description:
{Advanced Clarity}

A hero casts mass Mindshield (advanced) spell at the begining of each battle.

Costs 10 mana per battle and lasts until next week.

expert.description:
{Expert Clarity}

A hero casts expert Minshield spell at the begining of each battle.

Costs 10 mana per battle and lasts until next week.
